<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/57189573-yulia"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1627945538i/57189573._UY100_CR22,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/57189573-yulia">Yulia</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Books in this series can be read out of order. Every book is a stand alone story, even though the main characters remain the same. Most important deta<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Books in this series can be read out of order. Every book is a stand alone story, even though the main characters remain the same. Most important details are rehashed in every book to give readers a bit of a back story.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
